TITLE: Using Form.useWatch Hook with External API Integration
DESCRIPTION: Example demonstrating Form.useWatch hook to watch field values and integrate with external APIs using useSWR, automatically updating options when the watched field changes.
SOURCE: https://github.com/ant-design/ant-design/blob/master/components/form/index.en-US.md#2025-04-23_snippet_10

LANGUAGE: tsx
CODE:
```
const Demo = () => {
  const [form] = Form.useForm();
  const userName = Form.useWatch('username', form);

  const { data: options } = useSWR(`/api/user/${userName}`, fetcher);

  return (
    <Form form={form}>
      <Form.Item name="username">
        <AutoComplete options={options} />
      </Form.Item>
    </Form>
  );
};
```

